All parsers related to imports.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Import
    Represents a concrete import of a symbol, either via name or via ordinal.

    BoundImportSection

    Represents all imports from a single DLL.

    Represents the import section, fetches information about the data directory entries and their lookup table entries.

    Represents a lookup table entry.

    NameEntry

    NameImport
    Represents an import by name.
    NullEntry

    Instantiates an ordinal entry.
    OrdinalImport
